(firstQuint)Z-Drugs for Sleep Disorders in Alzheimer's Disease.

 Sleep disorders (SD) affects 35 to 50 percent of patients with AD.

 These disorders often make caring for patients at home very difficult.

 Zolpidem and Zoplicone are prescribed drugs for sleep disorder in AD patients.

